OL,3,CThree-year-old boy dies after falling
OL,4,Cin pond
OL,6,FA three-year-old boy has died after
OL,7,Ffalling into a pond.
OL,9,FEmergency services were called to an
OL,10,Faddress in Crosby on 18 July,
OL,11,Ffollowing reports that a young child
OL,12,Fhad fallen into the water.
OL,14,FMerseyside Police said its officers,
OL,15,Fand North West Ambulance Service,
OL,16,Fattended the scene on Brownmoor Lane
OL,17,Fbefore the toddler was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital where he died short time
OL,19,Flater.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/2
